Dark Finish his Cycle in the Cr chamber and exits out of the maximal base to 
the jungle.

Lion Finish its Cycle and has under a few changes Like metal claws fangs 
armor on its back it.

Liono Finish his Cycle in the Cr chamaber and goes to the main computer and 
leaves a message That Reads : 
Dear Iron, 
    Your in charge until I return.  Some of us lead. Some of us Follow. Some 
of us a Guardians that appear when need a fade without a trace. Until I find 
out what the matrix wants of me I will be on this Journey. So it maybe along 
time. Tell key I Love her.

As Liono Picks up his sword he starts to slip out of the base unnoticed the 
night air is cool heading north. "Which way?" 

A blue ball appear and Flies to the East. 

As Liono Heads east.

"RRRRRRRRRROOOOOOOOOOOAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAARRRRRRRRRRR"
It the white Lion Runs up to Liono nuzzles him.

Liono Laughs "So you want to come too well I guess you need a name how about 
Arokh"

Arokh nods. 

As the 2 continue east.
